assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">花式！</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9kpuJnC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9kpuJnC.gif&h=c1c29c8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AOXL09p.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAOXL09p.gif&h=da33a572&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P9O0kzY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP9O0kzY.gif&h=f7f52476&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GNTfvwM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGNTfvwM.jpg&h=6cb0c505&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z1DfvwN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz1DfvwN.jpg&h=6f8fb244&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2riOQwO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2riOQwO.jpg&h=074cd595&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uCaEXbO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuCaEXbO.jpg&h=0736be80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/shojk9N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fshojk9N.jpg&h=e87f4f61&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u72wcgs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu72wcgs.jpg&h=4e7ea801&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hdRT928.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhdRT928.jpg&h=fe5ef654&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KCfhVw9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKCfhVw9.jpg&h=cc4a2b71&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F6BpAxa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF6BpAxa.jpg&h=4f61ec87&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SRYWrDQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSRYWrDQ.jpg&h=7f1b8468&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G1orOSa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG1orOSa.jpg&h=6f8244b3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iOobZYR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiOobZYR.jpg&h=d87249b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n@期望連仔幫手壓制fake news <br />\n@上連登要用多用腦！<br />\n預備大型商場不合作運動：<br />\n齋睇唔買，儲多d錢；人多自然塞<br />\n連儂牆戰線不能倒！修建連儂，有你有我<br />\n<br />\n<ins>考驗毅力與堅持</ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">做更具價值嘅野</span><br />\n#離開同溫層，接觸各種人，理解佢地嘅想法，將不支持我們的人轉為支持我們！這是成功的方法！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />抗爭/革命搞十年八載唔出奇<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">衛城革命，生活抗爭；拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；</span><br />\n<em>每日任務：</em><br />\n1. 優先<span style=\"color: red;\">幫襯</span>良心商店<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">抵制</span>「邪惡」「無良」的商戶，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: red;\">免費港鐵</span>（注意安全）；二人同遊，一人免費；買平飛；長者八達通<br />\n4. 夜晚<span style=\"color: red;\">十點咆哮</span>！（改9點會少好多人）<br />\n5. <span style=\"color: red;\">健身+運動</span>，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n6. <span style=\"color: red;\">每日一post</span>，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests <br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86ra3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=d9099cd3\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n7. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n8. 保持<span style=\"color: red;\">獨立思考</span>，分析能力level up，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">冷處理fake news/ rumour</span></strong> 、五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n<em>每星期任務：</em><br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">低消費</span>，高儲蓄；罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">做孝子救港</span>，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去<span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆</span>貼3張文宣，輸出革命思想<br />\n<br />\n<em>每月任務：</em><br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股，MPF轉美國<br />\n2. 搵多一個人參與<br />\n3. 關心社會、陪審員、派傳單、放映會<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾；Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.14</blockquote>"},{"pid":"0ee0a14ce67371b08e71bb42a1e06ba67cf28d97","tid":1575001,"uid":272753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc248d1c0ae7ef05418af04e91891eb7a1f291ec","tid":1575001,"uid":285875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:04:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">又係我地 復仇閪 過往戰力包括:<br />\n登場處女作 拆大公招牌 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1355565\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1355565</a><br />\n召喚地政總署 清拆何妖祖墳 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1355662\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1355662</a><br />\n第三波 專業清算南邊圍一帶僭建物 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1367235\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1367235</a></span><br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n選舉期臨近, 一定有大量宣傳海報, 郵件入去你屋苑, 大廈同信箱。 事實上, 根據區議會選舉活動指引，候選人需要<strong>法團</strong>, <strong>業委會</strong>同<strong>物業管理公司</strong>要求簽一份文件叫做&quot;在私人物業展示選舉廣告或進行競選活動的批准書&quot; <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>攞批准入去宣傳</strong></span>。咁樣就可以擺法團，業委同管理公司上檯，同選舉委員會發信聲明唔比任何關於選舉的宣傳品，海報，同拉票活動進入屋苑，以保屋苑中立。<br />\n<br />\n但要<strong>業主</strong>迫到法團，業委同管理公司支持咁做，<ins>最簡單理由就係唔想屋苑混亂</ins>，咁就會有人支持。其次就係<ins>避免屋苑成為選舉工具</ins>，呢啲理由可以較多人支持，同夾到嗰班友都變中立。<br />\n<br />\n呢張批准書有一個特點係你可以就個別候選人比或唔比, 但基於保持公平, 唔建議選擇性去比候選人, 而係一視同仁。呢招可以令到藍絲宣傳死晒, 入唔到大廈同屋苑, 但當然如果有新晉黃絲想入宣傳品亦會比呢張批准書封殺。<br />\n<br />\n另外，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所有住戶有對其住用單位獨享佔用權</span></span></strong>，你<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">絕對可以唔比</span></strong></span>人去你屋企洗樓，透過屋苑或樓宇對講機拉票，甚或見到陌生候選人出入屋苑拉票，如果有，可以點做? 根據區議會<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">選舉活動指引第8章</span></strong>，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">8.18條</span></strong>，佢哋話明智做法係<span style=\"color: orange;\">先報管理處同報警</span>，然後如屬實，<span style=\"color: orange;\">選管會可發表聲明，嚴厲譴責或譴責有關候選人</span>。<br />\n<br />\n如果<strong>法團</strong>，<strong>管理公司大細超</strong>，咁點搞? 大家可以<span style=\"color: red;\">報比選管會知，而同樣會發表聲明作出譴責有關組織。</span><br />\n<br />\n隨帖附上2019新版 &lt;在私人物業展示選舉廣告或進行競選活動的批准書 &gt;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/2019dce/reo_c13_dc(2019).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2F2019dce%2Freo_c13_dc%282019%29.pdf&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86ra3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=a8cf627e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/2019dce/reo_c13_dc(2019).pdf</a><br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n由於我地既投訴個案有時會有D status update, 但又唔想開多個post 浪費大家時間<br />\n所以我地開左個facebook page 用黎update 過往既投訴case 情況, 亦都會有個好D 既平台同大家交流, 黎緊我地會做多少少物管方面既topic, 希望可以幫到大家, 踢走建制<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/revengehi/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frevengehi%2F&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86ra3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=cc1ed713\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/revengehi/</a><br />\n請大家多多支持<br />\n不日會有場好戲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>IF WE BURN, YOU BURN WITH US.<br />\n寧投熊熊烈火，光盡而滅。<br />\n不伴寂寂朽木，默然同腐。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n一群專業清算師上"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T17:29:58.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"db9b0842ef856939a3d36280fafd73f65fcea4ec","tid":1575001,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T17:38:48.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"5021f23ce56aabacb36f0cf18a6471f569f911eb","tid":15750